{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cc6709d6cd","title":"二师宜位于酯河城地域","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d82226f50f","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":2,"articleId":"cc6709d6cd"}],"tags":[{"id":"25e2abfb25","name":"李富春","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2d764ed7e0","type":"paragraph","text":"二师宜位于酯河城地域”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cc6709d6cd"},{"id":"1983e4001b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月2日）彭：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cc6709d6cd"},{"id":"68ddb96fa0","type":"paragraph","text":"胡宗南还在陇县一带。我二方面军将于一星期后转移至渭水以北。据李富春报，宁夏群众很好，马部恐悦，除少数据点外，大部围寨可不战而定，并有抢夺渡船之可能。似此二师宜即位置于码河城地域，以便待提草攻宁问题决定后，二师调动便利，不致过于疲劳。关于提早攻宁问题，请你提出意见。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cc6709d6cd"},{"id":"d9a7e502b2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cc6709d6cd"},{"id":"74192f158e","type":"paragraph","text":"二号十四时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cc6709d6cd"},{"id":"d8c7b0af24","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军第一方面军司令员、西方野战军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cc6709d6cd"},{"id":"fc773c4e44","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]李富春，当时任中共陕甘宁省委书记。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cc6709d6cd"},{"id":"76abf15c39","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]马，指马鸿速，当时任国民党军西北“汇”总司令部第一防守区（第十五路军）司令兼新编第七师师长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cc6709d6cd"},{"id":"572b903ad5","type":"paragraph","text":"[4]硝河城，镇名，位于今宁夏西吉县东南。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cc6709d6cd"}],"page":{"id":"c1a2ceb07c","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"cc6709d6cd","start":187,"end":187}}}},"__N_SSG":true}